## 🛠 Technical Stack

| Layer | Technology |
| :--- | :--- |
| **Framework** | Shopify Hydrogen (Remix) |
| **Runtime** | MiniOxygen (Cloudflare Workers) |
| **3D Engine** | Three.js |
| **Styling** | Tailwind CSS |
| **Payment** | Stripe (Fetch API Implementation) |
| **State Management** | React Context + LocalStorage Persistence |

